stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NavigateToGeoMap
    NavigateToGeoMap --> FetchGeoAlerts : GET /api/alerts/geo/
    FetchGeoAlerts --> LoadingMap
    LoadingMap --> RenderLeafletMap : Success
    LoadingMap --> ShowError : Failure
    RenderLeafletMap --> PlotMarkers : lat/lng coordinates
    PlotMarkers --> DisplayMap
    DisplayMap --> ClickMarker : User clicks pin
    ClickMarker --> ShowAlertPopup
    ShowAlertPopup --> DisplayMap
    DisplayMap --> [*]